WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.030
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.120 --> 01:35.780
[The 12th Xiangsheng High School Debate Final]

01:35.200 --> 01:36.479
This is the 12th Xiangsheng

01:35.780 --> 01:39.610
[2005]

01:36.560 --> 01:38.200
High School Debate Finals.

01:38.350 --> 01:39.759
The winning team is...

01:40.200 --> 01:41.150
Yuezhou No.3 High School.

01:41.150 --> 01:43.150
Please welcome the presenter
to award the certificates.

01:43.150 --> 01:44.210
Great! Wonderful!

01:47.509 --> 01:48.200
Congratulations.

01:48.200 --> 01:48.870
Thank you.

01:49.840 --> 01:50.350
Thanks.

01:50.759 --> 01:51.360
Congrats.

01:52.280 --> 01:54.280
You deserve credit
for this win too.

01:54.310 --> 01:56.950
The Best Debater of this competition is...

01:57.840 --> 02:01.170
Li Wenyue, the third debater
from Xianghu No.1 High School.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.000
Are they kidding?

02:04.430 --> 02:05.680
Our team is the champion.

02:05.680 --> 02:06.480
Congratulations.

02:06.480 --> 02:07.150
Thank you.

02:09.280 --> 02:09.910
The Best Debater award

02:09.910 --> 02:11.660
should have clearly gone to you.

02:11.660 --> 02:13.630
They must have pulled some strings.

02:13.630 --> 02:15.090
Is choice more important,

02:15.470 --> 02:16.560
or is hard work?

02:17.680 --> 02:18.750
Real life

02:19.030 --> 02:21.290
is much more complex than a debate topic.

02:21.630 --> 02:24.360
Looks, personality, family background...

02:24.910 --> 02:26.710
there are countless variables.

02:26.960 --> 02:29.520
You are competing
with others all the time.

02:29.100 --> 02:32.130
[Episode 9: You Don't Win or Lose
at the Starting Line]

02:33.520 --> 02:34.079
Mr. Wang.

02:33.950 --> 02:35.579
[Huaqing University Student Profile]

02:34.680 --> 02:35.360
Professor Xu

02:35.360 --> 02:37.120
is the head judge of this competition.

02:37.120 --> 02:39.030
It concerns a contestant's eligibility.

02:39.030 --> 02:40.520
I've explained the situation to him.

02:40.520 --> 02:41.750
I'd like his opinion.

02:42.000 --> 02:43.000
Everyone's here.

02:44.079 --> 02:44.630
Professor Xu.

02:44.630 --> 02:45.360
Please, have a seat.

02:45.360 --> 02:45.750
Okay.

02:46.150 --> 02:46.590
You're here.

02:46.590 --> 02:47.190
Wang,

02:47.910 --> 02:48.520
about the matter

02:48.520 --> 02:49.960
Section Chief Zhan told me about

02:49.960 --> 02:51.079
Contestant No.12,

02:51.280 --> 02:52.870
so I came to see what's going on.

02:52.870 --> 02:53.530
Take a look.

02:53.560 --> 02:53.890
Okay.

02:58.240 --> 02:59.040
Professor Xu.

02:59.870 --> 03:00.840
Xia scored a perfect score

03:00.840 --> 03:02.750
on the college entrance exam's
English paper.

03:02.750 --> 03:04.210
Based on past experience,

03:04.520 --> 03:05.590
rural students'

03:05.590 --> 03:07.360
conditions for learning English
aren't great.

03:07.360 --> 03:09.430
Their English scores
are generally not high.

03:09.430 --> 03:10.490
Even city students

03:10.560 --> 03:12.090
rarely get perfect scores.

03:12.230 --> 03:13.560
It's truly incredible.

03:14.310 --> 03:16.040
Not only is she a rural student,

03:16.220 --> 03:17.950
she also dropped out for 2 years

03:18.310 --> 03:20.240
and repeated a grade for just 1 year

03:20.240 --> 03:21.360
before she took the exam.

03:21.360 --> 03:22.420
With such results,

03:22.590 --> 03:24.960
she must be a born genius.

03:25.740 --> 03:26.390
Exactly.

03:26.870 --> 03:27.870
Judges, leaders,

03:27.910 --> 03:29.630
I am the team leader from Huaqing.

03:29.630 --> 03:30.910
Xia Xiaolan is an outstanding student

03:30.910 --> 03:32.310
in our Architecture Department.

03:32.310 --> 03:33.750
She ranks first every semester.

03:33.750 --> 03:35.360
Her English grades have always been good.

03:35.360 --> 03:36.750
She has no problems when it comes to

03:36.750 --> 03:37.590
communicating with foreign architects.

03:37.590 --> 03:38.720
I can vouch for this.

03:38.870 --> 03:40.000
You are her teacher.

03:40.240 --> 03:41.840
Of course you'd protect her.

03:42.000 --> 03:42.590
Mr. Wang,

03:42.750 --> 03:44.680
Xia Xiaolan is truly outstanding.

03:46.280 --> 03:47.240
How did I end up with

03:47.240 --> 03:48.630
an idiot like you?

03:48.630 --> 03:49.520
Stop hitting him.

03:49.520 --> 03:50.800
Why are you beating the child?

03:50.800 --> 03:52.190
A blank letter of introduction.

03:52.190 --> 03:54.390
Is that something you can just hand out?

03:55.280 --> 03:56.030
I

03:56.520 --> 03:57.579
work in education,

03:57.800 --> 03:59.120
and my son got expelled.

03:59.120 --> 04:00.240
How am I supposed to

04:00.240 --> 04:01.500
show my face in public?

04:03.310 --> 04:04.360
It's all because of Xia Ziyu,

04:04.360 --> 04:05.590
that little tramp.

04:06.400 --> 04:06.840
Mom.

04:08.030 --> 04:09.310
You can't blame Ziyu.

04:09.910 --> 04:11.370
She was forced into it too.

04:11.910 --> 04:14.040
If you want to blame someone, blame...

04:16.000 --> 04:17.190
Xia Xiaolan.

04:18.480 --> 04:19.339
As far as I know,

04:19.920 --> 04:20.800
her family background

04:20.800 --> 04:21.730
is very complex.

04:22.310 --> 04:24.170
She has a family member in prison.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.040
She also has

04:25.040 --> 04:26.720
a sister who attended college for a year

04:26.720 --> 04:27.980
that is now a fugitive.

04:28.240 --> 04:30.240
With a family background like that,

04:30.390 --> 04:32.320
how could she make it to the finals?

04:35.120 --> 04:35.950
To the audience here

04:35.950 --> 04:36.920
and those

04:36.920 --> 04:37.750
watching on TV,

04:37.750 --> 04:38.390
hello.

04:38.510 --> 04:40.190
This is the venue
of the first National College Student

04:40.190 --> 04:42.240
English Competition finals.

04:42.560 --> 04:43.750
This final brings together

04:43.750 --> 04:45.270
16 contestants

04:45.270 --> 04:47.040
from universities across the country.

04:47.040 --> 04:47.800
After each contestant

04:47.800 --> 04:49.120
finishes all rounds,

04:49.190 --> 04:51.159
the judges will score them.

04:51.630 --> 04:52.620
Among the 5 judges,

04:52.620 --> 04:54.600
we will drop the highest
and lowest scores.

04:54.600 --> 04:55.920
The resulting average

04:55.920 --> 04:58.050
will be the contestant's final score.

04:58.190 --> 05:00.800
Now, let the competition officially begin.

05:01.000 --> 05:01.870
Hello, everyone.

05:01.870 --> 05:02.920
I am Zhao Qingsong

05:03.190 --> 05:04.950
from Huxin University.

05:05.070 --> 05:06.070
I feel honored...

05:06.070 --> 05:07.510
My name is Wang Xinxin.

05:07.630 --> 05:09.920
I'm glad to participate

05:10.070 --> 05:11.240
in this competition.

05:11.240 --> 05:14.190
To master English...

05:15.120 --> 05:15.510
Okay.

05:15.510 --> 05:16.390
After dropping the highest

05:16.390 --> 05:17.310
and lowest scores,

05:17.310 --> 05:18.910
contestant No.11's score is

05:18.920 --> 05:20.270
93.6 points.

05:20.430 --> 05:22.310
Now, please welcome contestant No.12,

05:22.310 --> 05:24.800
Xia Xiaolan from Huaqing University.

05:31.240 --> 05:32.070
Go, Xiaolan!

05:45.000 --> 05:46.040
Hello, everyone.

05:46.159 --> 05:47.240
I am Xia Xiaolan,

05:47.409 --> 05:48.970
contestant No.12

05:49.040 --> 05:50.630
from Huaqing University.

05:51.070 --> 05:51.920
This morning,

05:52.270 --> 05:54.000
someone called me incredible.

05:54.190 --> 05:54.870
So now,

05:55.000 --> 05:55.950
let me show the incredible me

05:55.950 --> 05:57.390
to you.

05:57.920 --> 05:58.560
There is no such thing as

05:58.560 --> 05:59.680
an unbelievable genius.

05:58.690 --> 06:01.420
[Half an hour ago]

06:00.000 --> 06:01.200
She must be cheating.

06:01.680 --> 06:02.360
We should disqualify

06:02.360 --> 06:03.630
her from the competition.

06:03.630 --> 06:04.560
On what grounds?

06:05.870 --> 06:06.400
Xiaolan.

06:06.830 --> 06:07.830
I can handle this.

06:09.070 --> 06:10.400
You must be Xia Xiaolan.

06:12.630 --> 06:13.560
So, Mr. Wang,

06:13.720 --> 06:15.250
you've never met me before.

06:16.060 --> 06:16.630
Then why

06:16.630 --> 06:18.430
can you state with such certainty

06:18.430 --> 06:19.760
that my results are fake

06:19.870 --> 06:21.240
and disqualify me?

06:22.430 --> 06:23.430
I know your family

06:23.720 --> 06:24.580
and your sister

06:24.800 --> 06:25.750
very well.

06:25.870 --> 06:27.130
Since you know so much,

06:27.600 --> 06:28.930
you should know clearly

06:29.070 --> 06:29.720
that my cousin

06:29.720 --> 06:31.310
became a fugitive

06:31.680 --> 06:33.040
because she instigated someone

06:33.040 --> 06:34.310
to intentionally hurt me

06:34.310 --> 06:36.560
and stop me
from taking the college entrance exam.

06:36.560 --> 06:37.480
So what?

06:38.000 --> 06:38.920
With a family like that,

06:38.920 --> 06:40.750
what kind of person can they raise?

06:40.750 --> 06:42.280
Everyone knows the answer.

06:43.000 --> 06:43.600
Is that so?

06:44.360 --> 06:45.360
If Mr. Wang

06:45.360 --> 06:46.510
thinks that way,

06:47.070 --> 06:48.930
then may I take the liberty to ask,

06:49.000 --> 06:50.510
your son, Wang Jianhua,

06:50.750 --> 06:52.240
broke the rules
to issue a letter of introduction

06:52.240 --> 06:53.900
and helped a criminal escape.

06:54.190 --> 06:55.310
So shouldn't I

06:55.310 --> 06:56.270
also question

06:56.630 --> 06:57.480
your family's

06:57.480 --> 06:59.010
character and upbringing?

07:00.160 --> 07:01.290
Jianhua was forced!

07:01.700 --> 07:03.100
He didn't know anything.

07:03.190 --> 07:04.870
It was you sisters who ruined him!

07:04.870 --> 07:06.330
Then how would I have known

07:06.430 --> 07:07.800
about my sister's crime?

07:07.800 --> 07:08.750
I am a victim too.

07:09.720 --> 07:11.040
Judges, you all saw it.

07:11.680 --> 07:13.240
It is Mr. Wang Guangping

07:13.760 --> 07:15.040
trying to retaliate against me

07:15.040 --> 07:16.700
because of personal grudges.

07:17.800 --> 07:18.600
Professor Xu,

07:18.870 --> 07:20.000
the competition is about to start.

07:20.000 --> 07:21.000
What do you think?

07:27.270 --> 07:28.240
I think...

07:28.830 --> 07:29.690
How about this?

07:30.390 --> 07:31.390
Miss Xia Xiaolan,

07:32.470 --> 07:35.040
I agree to let you continue
in the competition.

07:35.040 --> 07:35.680
However,

07:36.070 --> 07:37.070
since your appearance here

07:37.070 --> 07:39.000
broke the rule that contestants

07:39.210 --> 07:39.800
and judges cannot communicate

07:39.800 --> 07:41.360
before the competition.

07:41.920 --> 07:43.120
Your performance just now

07:43.120 --> 07:44.390
has already left an impression

07:44.390 --> 07:45.390
on all the judges.

07:45.630 --> 07:46.120
Because of this,

07:46.120 --> 07:47.040
it is unfair

07:47.040 --> 07:48.120
to the other contestants.

07:48.120 --> 07:49.380
You admit this, right?

07:49.800 --> 07:50.270
Yes,

07:50.510 --> 07:51.120
I admit it.

07:51.630 --> 07:52.070
Good.

07:52.950 --> 07:53.680
In that case,

07:54.070 --> 07:54.920
in the competition venue,

07:54.920 --> 07:56.750
I will personally set a question for you.

07:56.750 --> 07:58.040
Whether you have real skill

07:58.040 --> 07:59.430
or if there's something fishy,

07:59.430 --> 08:01.120
we'll find out at the venue.

08:01.750 --> 08:03.610
Do you dare accept the challenge?

08:05.040 --> 08:06.240
I have a clear conscience.

08:06.240 --> 08:07.170
Of course I dare.

08:07.870 --> 08:08.600
Xia Xiaolan,

08:09.250 --> 08:10.980
how do you feel about fairness?

08:11.560 --> 08:12.310
Do you think

08:12.560 --> 08:14.620
there is true fairness in this world?

08:17.240 --> 08:17.950
I believe

08:18.560 --> 08:21.390
fairness is the scale in our heart.

08:22.000 --> 08:23.560
And the tilt of the scale

08:23.560 --> 08:24.400
is determined

08:24.430 --> 08:27.190
by our cognition and experiences.

08:27.950 --> 08:28.870
I believe

08:29.040 --> 08:31.680
with my persistence and integrity,

08:32.030 --> 08:34.840
fairness will eventually come to me.

08:35.270 --> 08:36.960
I think I am fortunate.

08:37.200 --> 08:40.600
Because I can prove my abilities
by taking part

08:40.669 --> 08:42.270
in this public competition.

08:43.200 --> 08:44.670
However, many people

08:44.670 --> 08:46.670
have no such opportunity.

08:47.750 --> 08:49.600
They're broken away from fairness

08:49.600 --> 08:51.870
because of their backgrounds or fates.

08:53.840 --> 08:55.360
I hope more people

08:55.390 --> 08:57.910
can be openminded, generous,

08:57.910 --> 08:59.910
and let go of the prejudice,

09:00.200 --> 09:02.320
so that the real fairness

09:02.510 --> 09:03.630
may come true.

09:04.120 --> 09:06.550
That day may still be far away,

09:06.870 --> 09:09.440
but I am looking forward to it.

09:09.790 --> 09:10.390
Thank you.

09:15.630 --> 09:17.390
Excellent!

09:32.410 --> 09:32.810
Okay.

09:32.840 --> 09:34.030
Thank you, Xia Xiaolan,

09:34.030 --> 09:34.910
for that wonderful performance.

09:34.910 --> 09:35.480
Now, let's ask

09:35.480 --> 09:36.080
our judges

09:36.080 --> 09:37.290
to score Xiaolan.

09:37.600 --> 09:38.550
Thank you for

09:38.550 --> 09:39.320
your wonderful performance.

09:39.320 --> 09:40.120
Now judges,

09:40.150 --> 09:41.550
please show your scores.

09:42.790 --> 09:43.670
Professor Catherine

09:43.670 --> 09:45.670
gave 98.9.

09:47.810 --> 09:48.570
Ms. Chen Min

09:48.600 --> 09:50.390
gave 97.6.

09:50.770 --> 09:51.720
Professor Xu Guozhang

09:51.720 --> 09:53.690
gave 98.2.

09:53.720 --> 09:54.720
Mr. Zheng Zheng

09:54.720 --> 09:56.600
gave 98.4.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.930
And our Mr. Zhang Tianjing

09:57.930 --> 09:59.720
gave 98.

10:04.480 --> 10:04.910
So,

10:04.930 --> 10:05.810
Xia Xiaolan's

10:05.840 --> 10:06.870
final score is

10:06.960 --> 10:08.550
98.2.

10:08.600 --> 10:10.400
She is currently in first place.

10:13.790 --> 10:14.480
The final score

10:14.480 --> 10:15.360
is

10:15.480 --> 10:17.670
98.2.

10:17.750 --> 10:20.480
Congratulations, for being in first place.

10:22.680 --> 10:23.210
Okay.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.270
Next, let's welcome

10:24.270 --> 10:25.600
contestant No.13.

10:26.120 --> 10:27.750
Next, let's welcome

10:27.750 --> 10:29.080
contestant No.13.

10:34.270 --> 10:34.960
Mr. Wang.

10:40.390 --> 10:42.000
Don't think this is over.

10:42.720 --> 10:43.840
I am the supervisor

10:43.840 --> 10:44.840
of this competition.

10:44.840 --> 10:45.770
I have to sign off

10:45.840 --> 10:47.080
on the final results.

10:47.790 --> 10:48.390
Mr. Wang,

10:48.960 --> 10:50.030
do you think that after I exposed

10:50.030 --> 10:51.510
our personal grudge,

10:51.870 --> 10:53.870
you are still qualified to sign off?

10:54.670 --> 10:55.800
You have no evidence

10:56.150 --> 10:57.210
to prove I cheated,

10:57.570 --> 10:58.840
but I have the ability to prove

10:58.840 --> 10:59.480
that I am qualified

10:59.480 --> 11:00.550
to be on that stage.

11:01.510 --> 11:03.440
From the moment you questioned me,

11:03.600 --> 11:04.800
you had already lost.

11:06.550 --> 11:07.550
It's not over yet.

11:08.200 --> 11:10.670
Neither of us knows who the winner is.

11:11.510 --> 11:13.270
Xia Ziyu didn't admit defeat either,

11:13.270 --> 11:14.670
so she became a fugitive.

11:15.150 --> 11:16.350
You are just like her—

11:16.510 --> 11:17.570
just as shameless.

11:17.960 --> 11:18.510
You assume

11:18.510 --> 11:19.970
everyone is just like you.

11:20.150 --> 11:21.270
But sorry,

11:21.600 --> 11:22.550
I, Xia Xiaolan,

11:22.720 --> 11:24.080
rely on my own abilities

11:24.080 --> 11:25.340
to get where I am today.

11:25.670 --> 11:26.910
Your crooked ways

11:27.150 --> 11:28.240
can't stop me.

11:28.720 --> 11:29.480
Because of you, Jianhua

11:29.480 --> 11:30.810
can't even go to school.

11:31.030 --> 11:33.270
Why should you
have a better life than him?

11:33.270 --> 11:35.130
I won't let you get away with this.

11:35.390 --> 11:36.600
Dropping the highest

11:36.720 --> 11:37.870
and the lowest score...

11:37.870 --> 11:38.240
Okay.

11:38.240 --> 11:39.360
Our contestant No.16's

11:39.360 --> 11:40.480
final score is

11:40.630 --> 11:42.240
97.3 points.

11:45.720 --> 11:46.250
Xiaolan,

11:47.550 --> 11:48.270
go and accept

11:48.270 --> 11:49.930
the honor that belongs to you.

11:50.380 --> 11:50.840
Okay.

11:57.240 --> 11:57.770
Mr. Wang,

11:58.720 --> 11:59.600
you can no longer change

11:59.600 --> 12:01.030
the result of the competition.

12:01.030 --> 12:01.600
If you still have

12:01.600 --> 12:02.930
a shred of rationality,

12:03.150 --> 12:04.560
save yourself some dignity.

12:04.560 --> 12:08.640
[The Finals Of The First National College English Competition Of The Chengrong Cup]

12:04.670 --> 12:05.440
And now,

12:05.750 --> 12:07.030
the winner of
the First National College Student

12:07.030 --> 12:08.750
English Competition Finals

12:08.840 --> 12:09.910
has been decided.

12:10.120 --> 12:10.760
She is

12:10.790 --> 12:12.080
contestant No.12

12:12.080 --> 12:13.080
from Huaqing University,

12:13.080 --> 12:14.030
Xia Xiaolan.

12:14.480 --> 12:16.230
See? I told you our Xiaolan

12:16.320 --> 12:18.180
would definitely be first place.

12:52.360 --> 12:53.080
Who are you?

12:53.550 --> 12:54.880
Who do you think you are?

12:55.200 --> 12:56.060
Let me tell you,

12:56.550 --> 12:57.750
without my sign-off,

12:57.870 --> 12:59.670
Xia Xiaolan is nothing.

12:59.790 --> 13:01.120
What an abuse of power.

13:02.600 --> 13:03.600
How about

13:03.720 --> 13:04.780
I sign it off, then?

13:05.120 --> 13:05.960
Minister Tang,

13:05.960 --> 13:06.890
why are you here?

13:06.910 --> 13:09.150
The Ministry sent you
to supervise the competition,

13:09.150 --> 13:10.720
not to throw your weight around

13:10.720 --> 13:12.320
and settle personal grudges.

13:12.320 --> 13:13.200
If Zhan hadn't

13:13.600 --> 13:14.120
sent someone in time

13:14.120 --> 13:15.850
to tell me what's going on here,

13:16.070 --> 13:16.670
I'm afraid

13:17.120 --> 13:18.480
this first English competition

13:18.480 --> 13:20.200
would have been the last.

13:20.420 --> 13:21.550
Minister Tang, you don't know,

13:21.550 --> 13:22.240
this Xia Xiaolan,

13:22.240 --> 13:22.870
there's definitely
something wrong with her—

13:22.870 --> 13:23.800
Wang Guangping,

13:24.240 --> 13:25.170
watch yourself.

13:25.510 --> 13:26.840
Have you lost your mind?

13:27.030 --> 13:27.480
Yes,

13:28.000 --> 13:28.930
I've gone crazy.

13:29.120 --> 13:30.450
I went crazy 4 years ago.

13:30.600 --> 13:32.110
They ruined my son's life,

13:32.440 --> 13:33.600
so I'm going to ruin theirs!

13:33.600 --> 13:34.000
You...

13:34.510 --> 13:37.200
No one can ruin anyone else's life.

13:38.000 --> 13:40.080
We all walk our own paths.

13:40.510 --> 13:41.320
Are you the one questioning

13:41.320 --> 13:42.050
our Xiaolan?

13:44.600 --> 13:46.000
Who do you think you are?

13:46.720 --> 13:47.670
I'm telling you,

13:48.240 --> 13:50.210
as a village girl, it's not easy

13:50.240 --> 13:51.600
that Xiaolan made it here

13:51.600 --> 13:52.550
step by step.

13:53.240 --> 13:54.270
She suffered

13:54.270 --> 13:55.320
and toiled.

13:55.910 --> 13:57.390
Yet she has to be sabotaged
by someone like you—

13:57.390 --> 13:58.450
a malicious

13:58.480 --> 14:00.030
and narrow-minded man

14:00.030 --> 14:01.510
making things difficult for her.

14:01.510 --> 14:02.970
But she never complained!

14:03.290 --> 14:04.840
You failed to raise your own child well,

14:04.840 --> 14:06.840
so you take it out on a young girl.

14:07.220 --> 14:09.170
Reflect on your own issues.

14:09.200 --> 14:10.270
Ma'am, Ma'am.

14:10.290 --> 14:11.290
Please calm down.

14:12.090 --> 14:12.670
We will make sure

14:12.670 --> 14:14.050
we will be fair towards Ms. Xia

14:14.050 --> 14:14.980
for this matter.

14:15.270 --> 14:16.270
We all saw Xiaolan's performance

14:16.270 --> 14:17.390
today.

14:17.720 --> 14:19.320
You don't need to be fair to her.

14:19.320 --> 14:20.580
She earned it herself.

14:25.510 --> 14:26.720
Let's give another round of applause

14:26.720 --> 14:27.510
to our second

14:27.510 --> 14:29.200
and third-place winners.

14:30.150 --> 14:32.080
Students, you may leave the stage.

14:32.360 --> 14:33.120
Now we have arrived at

14:33.120 --> 14:34.960
the most exciting moment of the day.

14:34.960 --> 14:35.960
Let's once again

14:36.170 --> 14:38.170
welcome today's champion,

14:38.200 --> 14:40.790
Xia Xiaolan from Huaqing University.

14:42.080 --> 14:43.270
Let's welcome

14:43.270 --> 14:44.600
Professor Xu Guozhang

14:44.630 --> 14:46.120
and Mr. Du Zhaohui

14:46.120 --> 14:47.030
from Chengrong Group

14:47.030 --> 14:48.830
to present the award to Xiaolan.

14:57.580 --> 14:59.580
[Certificate of Honor]

14:58.090 --> 14:59.150
Congratulations.

15:00.720 --> 15:01.790
Were you not afraid

15:02.120 --> 15:03.960
of offending me
with what you said just now?

15:03.960 --> 15:04.390
No.

15:04.840 --> 15:06.510
I trust you are fair.

15:07.190 --> 15:07.870
Xiaolan,

15:08.080 --> 15:09.610
you really are one of a kind.

15:09.760 --> 15:10.360
Thank you.

15:13.670 --> 15:14.400
Pretty girl,

15:14.510 --> 15:15.670
you've got a bright future.

15:15.670 --> 15:16.270
Thank you.

15:19.080 --> 15:20.240
I believe at this moment

15:20.240 --> 15:21.480
Xiaolan has a lot

15:21.480 --> 15:22.750
she wants to share with us.

15:22.750 --> 15:23.240
Please.

15:26.390 --> 15:27.510
First of all,

15:27.510 --> 15:29.480
I am very happy to receive this award.

15:29.480 --> 15:30.960
I want to thank my university,

15:30.960 --> 15:32.750
Huaqing University, for nurturing me.

15:32.750 --> 15:33.600
I want to thank my teachers

15:33.600 --> 15:35.080
for their dedicated guidance.

15:35.080 --> 15:36.440
And I want to thank our country

15:36.440 --> 15:37.910
for its growing prosperity,

15:37.910 --> 15:38.830
which gave me the opportunity

15:38.830 --> 15:39.990
to learn English.

15:40.480 --> 15:41.750
I also thank the judges here

15:41.750 --> 15:43.960
who always strive for fairness,

15:44.210 --> 15:45.240
for giving me a chance

15:45.240 --> 15:46.720
to prove myself.

15:47.150 --> 15:47.720
Finally,

15:47.960 --> 15:49.420
I want to thank my enemies.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.600
It is because of them

15:50.600 --> 15:52.200
that I never let my guard down

15:52.440 --> 15:54.480
and keep moving forward.

15:54.790 --> 15:55.390
Thank you.

15:58.820 --> 15:59.240
Very well.

15:59.240 --> 16:00.720
Thank you, Xiaolan,
for that wonderful speech.

16:00.720 --> 16:01.480
And here,

16:01.480 --> 16:02.550
I would also like to thank

16:02.550 --> 16:04.240
all the teachers and students present

16:04.240 --> 16:06.000
for supporting the Chengrong Cup.

16:06.000 --> 16:06.600
I declare

16:06.790 --> 16:09.030
the Finals Of The First National College English Competition

16:09.030 --> 16:10.160
Of The Chengrong Cup

16:10.320 --> 16:11.780
successfully concluded!

16:12.910 --> 16:13.960
We would also like to invite

16:13.960 --> 16:14.790
all students and teachers

16:14.790 --> 16:16.990
to come onto the stage for a group photo.

16:26.910 --> 16:27.630
Please make some space for me.

16:27.630 --> 16:28.600
Thank you.

16:29.200 --> 16:30.260
Get ready. Come on.

16:30.550 --> 16:31.120
Ms. Xia,

16:31.390 --> 16:32.450
congratulations.

16:32.810 --> 16:33.240
Thank you.

16:33.240 --> 16:34.170
Okay, get ready.

16:35.440 --> 16:36.080
Look here.

16:37.000 --> 16:38.910
3, 2, 1.

16:39.600 --> 16:40.460
Okay, one more.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.130
Look at me. Here.

16:42.600 --> 16:43.840
3, 2, 1.

16:44.480 --> 16:44.870
Okay.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.270
Perfect.

16:46.790 --> 16:48.990
Thank you for your hard work, everyone.

16:49.030 --> 16:49.600
Xiaolan,

16:49.600 --> 16:50.850
your English is amazing.

16:50.850 --> 16:51.550
How did you practice?

16:51.550 --> 16:52.120
Yeah, exactly.

16:52.120 --> 16:53.600
We want to learn from you.

16:53.600 --> 16:54.320
Let's communicate.

16:54.320 --> 16:55.510
I'm from Huaqing University.

16:55.510 --> 16:56.630
You can send letters to me.

16:56.630 --> 16:57.550
I will receive them.

16:57.550 --> 16:58.960
Okay, we'll write to you often.

16:58.960 --> 16:59.840
Let's keep in touch.

16:59.840 --> 17:00.550
Okay. Bye-bye!

17:00.550 --> 17:01.120
-Let's go.
-Bye-bye!

17:01.120 --> 17:01.720
Ms. Xia...

17:04.400 --> 17:04.800
You...

17:05.200 --> 17:05.730
Xiaolan,

17:06.440 --> 17:07.200
congratulations.

17:07.200 --> 17:07.720
What are you doing?

17:07.720 --> 17:08.750
This is too much.

17:08.960 --> 17:09.750
I have to be.

17:09.930 --> 17:11.589
You even gave them your mailing address.

17:11.589 --> 17:13.240
First letters, then mutual encouragement,

17:13.240 --> 17:14.790
and then studying together—

17:14.790 --> 17:16.589
I know this routine all too well.

17:17.640 --> 17:18.900
Do you want some water?

17:19.480 --> 17:20.589
Are you thirsty?

17:22.160 --> 17:23.290
I want to talk to her.

17:24.790 --> 17:25.200
Her?

17:25.920 --> 17:27.270
I think I just saw

17:27.550 --> 17:28.880
Mrs. Guan. Was she here?

17:29.310 --> 17:29.590
Yes.

17:29.880 --> 17:30.880
Grandma is here too.

17:30.880 --> 17:31.400
They were

17:31.400 --> 17:33.290
defending you against everyone just now too.

17:33.290 --> 17:34.640
Excuse me!

17:35.000 --> 17:36.750
My boss,

17:36.750 --> 17:38.350
who sponsored this contest,

17:38.720 --> 17:39.830
would like to have a chat with you.

17:39.830 --> 17:41.000
The one in white.

17:41.480 --> 17:43.010
After all, he paid for this.

17:43.330 --> 17:44.550
Please show some respect.

17:44.550 --> 17:45.510
He is the boss.

17:46.400 --> 17:46.750
Sure.

17:50.180 --> 17:51.750
Wait here.

17:53.110 --> 17:54.000
Hello, Mr. Du.

17:54.030 --> 17:55.090
What's the matter?

17:55.720 --> 17:56.270
Ms. Xia,

17:56.600 --> 17:57.240
you are even prettier offstage

17:57.240 --> 17:58.200
than on stage.

17:58.590 --> 18:00.320
Why don't we go somewhere quiet

18:00.350 --> 18:00.950
for a chat?

18:02.000 --> 18:02.600
Thank you.

18:02.830 --> 18:04.030
Let's just talk here.

18:04.640 --> 18:05.370
Want a smoke?

18:05.880 --> 18:06.510
No, thanks.

18:06.510 --> 18:07.310
I don't smoke.

18:08.030 --> 18:08.760
That's good.

18:11.750 --> 18:13.810
Are you really Xia Dajun's daughter?

18:17.110 --> 18:18.110
Go, Young Master!

18:18.110 --> 18:18.640
Hurry up.

18:18.720 --> 18:19.640
Come on, go!

18:28.960 --> 18:30.200
-Kun!
-Kun, Kun!

18:30.240 --> 18:31.270
You're hurt.

18:31.270 --> 18:31.720
Dajun.

18:32.240 --> 18:33.350
Protect Young Master.

18:33.350 --> 18:34.270
Protect Young Master.

18:34.270 --> 18:34.720
Okay.

18:35.240 --> 18:36.300
Get him out of here!

18:36.720 --> 18:37.350
Hurry, Kun!

18:37.350 --> 18:37.790
Go!

18:45.160 --> 18:45.960
Get in the car!

18:46.720 --> 18:47.120
Hurry!

18:47.160 --> 18:47.560
Hurry!

18:47.830 --> 18:48.240
Go!

19:06.720 --> 19:07.520
You're awake.

19:12.510 --> 19:13.040
Lie down.

19:15.400 --> 19:16.460
You worked for Kun?

19:20.240 --> 19:21.160
Kun is gone.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.940
Work for me from now on.

19:25.240 --> 19:25.960
I don't care

19:25.960 --> 19:27.090
where you came from.

19:27.480 --> 19:28.510
Since you saved me,

19:28.510 --> 19:29.640
I'll treat you well.

19:30.440 --> 19:31.970
Just rest and heal up first.

19:32.640 --> 19:33.900
Do you have any family?

19:34.510 --> 19:36.240
I can help take care of them too.

19:37.400 --> 19:37.720
I...

19:38.830 --> 19:40.720
I have a daughter.

19:42.200 --> 19:44.400
She's studying at Huaqing University.

19:45.400 --> 19:46.440
When he told me,

19:46.550 --> 19:48.040
I thought his brain was damaged.

19:48.040 --> 19:48.590
I didn't expect

19:48.590 --> 19:50.510
someone like you to actually exist.

19:50.510 --> 19:51.160
Mr. Du.

19:51.480 --> 19:52.880
What exactly do you want?

19:53.350 --> 19:54.750
It's about what you want.

19:54.920 --> 19:55.850
He saved my life.

19:56.000 --> 19:57.460
Just tell me what you want.

19:57.640 --> 19:59.300
Whether it's a job in Gangdao,

19:59.350 --> 20:00.480
residency,

20:00.640 --> 20:02.830
or even going abroad—
I can help you with them.

20:02.830 --> 20:03.110
Mr. Du—

20:03.110 --> 20:03.960
But looking at you,

20:03.960 --> 20:05.090
you're so beautiful

20:05.160 --> 20:06.090
and articulate.

20:06.510 --> 20:07.640
Why not go to Gangdao

20:07.750 --> 20:08.720
to join a beauty pageant,

20:08.720 --> 20:10.380
become a charity ambassador,

20:10.510 --> 20:12.110
and then become a movie star?

20:12.240 --> 20:13.000
It's a glamorous life.

20:13.000 --> 20:13.480
No need.

20:13.960 --> 20:15.220
Thanks for your offer.

20:15.350 --> 20:17.000
My parents divorced a long time ago.

20:17.000 --> 20:17.680
Xia Dajun and I

20:17.680 --> 20:18.830
have no contact.

20:19.350 --> 20:20.480
If something happens to him,

20:20.480 --> 20:21.830
I'll fulfill my duty to support him,

20:21.830 --> 20:23.750
but I don't care about anything else.

20:23.750 --> 20:24.200
Also,

20:24.400 --> 20:25.350
I don't need

20:25.400 --> 20:26.800
him arranging my future.

20:26.830 --> 20:28.880
And I don't want to
go to Gangdao in the future.

20:28.880 --> 20:29.110
Well...

20:29.110 --> 20:30.840
Is there anything else, Mr. Du?

20:31.510 --> 20:32.590
If there's nothing else,

20:32.590 --> 20:33.390
I'll be going.

20:33.680 --> 20:34.740
Let's go, Xiaolan.

20:35.720 --> 20:36.880
This is my boyfriend,

20:36.880 --> 20:37.540
Zhou Cheng.

20:42.640 --> 20:43.440
Young Master.

20:43.510 --> 20:44.680
She rejected you.

20:46.310 --> 20:47.200
Xia Dajun

20:47.240 --> 20:48.400
can give birth

20:48.400 --> 20:49.800
to such a smart daughter?

20:50.440 --> 20:51.270
Keep tabs on her news.

20:51.270 --> 20:52.590
She's graduating soon.

20:52.590 --> 20:53.920
I want to see what career

20:54.000 --> 20:55.200
is better than being a star

20:55.200 --> 20:55.860
in Gangdao.

20:55.920 --> 20:57.550
Sure thing. Leave it to me.

20:59.480 --> 21:00.510
My grandma goes to bed early,

21:00.510 --> 21:02.110
so my mom took her home first.

21:02.350 --> 21:02.920
By the way,

21:02.920 --> 21:04.350
she said she'll throw you
a proper celebration

21:04.350 --> 21:05.720
this weekend at home.

21:06.500 --> 21:07.850
Why didn't you tell me

21:07.880 --> 21:10.010
that your mom and grandma were coming?

21:10.070 --> 21:11.830
I wanted to surprise you.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.460
But it turned into a shock, didn't it?

21:14.830 --> 21:15.440
Not at all.

21:15.720 --> 21:17.200
They think you were very brave.

21:17.200 --> 21:18.660
They're very proud of you.

21:18.680 --> 21:20.510
Why weren't you angry

21:20.640 --> 21:22.640
when that sponsor reached out to me?

21:23.160 --> 21:24.360
Why should I be angry?

21:30.270 --> 21:31.310
That guy just now

21:31.310 --> 21:32.880
said he's Xia Dajun's boss.

21:33.000 --> 21:33.720
He asked if I wanted

21:33.720 --> 21:35.270
to use my employee benefits.

21:35.270 --> 21:36.550
He said he'd send me to Gangdao

21:36.550 --> 21:37.640
to be a movie star.

21:40.890 --> 21:41.850
A movie star?

21:42.510 --> 21:44.070
You didn't refuse, did you?

21:45.510 --> 21:46.790
Why would I go to Gangdao?

21:46.790 --> 21:47.960
My application for early graduation

21:47.960 --> 21:49.020
has been approved.

21:49.070 --> 21:50.480
I'm going all the way south

21:50.480 --> 21:52.140
and build up the special zone!

21:54.190 --> 21:58.010
[Longcheng] [Jingcheng]

22:02.910 --> 22:06.530
[Longcheng Station]

22:23.350 --> 22:24.160
Yong!

22:25.310 --> 22:26.070
Are they almost here?

22:26.070 --> 22:26.930
Any minute now.

22:39.240 --> 22:39.840
Over here!

22:39.960 --> 22:40.640
Over here!

22:41.000 --> 22:41.680
Xiaolan!

22:41.830 --> 22:42.680
Bai!

22:46.350 --> 22:47.160
Uncle!

22:51.030 --> 22:51.480
Sorry, sorry.

22:51.480 --> 22:51.880
Hey!

22:52.350 --> 22:53.200
Xiaolan!

22:54.440 --> 22:55.480
Let me introduce you.

22:55.480 --> 22:56.680
This is my mom, Liu Fen.

22:56.680 --> 22:57.070
Hello, Ma'am.

22:57.070 --> 22:57.440
Hello.

22:57.440 --> 22:57.970
And this

22:58.000 --> 22:59.600
is my boyfriend, Zhou Cheng.

23:00.070 --> 23:01.670
Hello, Comrade Bai Zhenzhu.

23:01.790 --> 23:02.590
Hello, hello.

23:02.920 --> 23:04.550
I've heard Xiaolan mention you often.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.350
No need to be so formal.

23:05.350 --> 23:06.200
Just call me Sis Bai.

23:06.200 --> 23:06.660
Sis Bai.

23:07.640 --> 23:08.640
This is my good friend,

23:08.640 --> 23:09.030
Kang Wei.

23:09.030 --> 23:09.750
Hello, hello.

23:09.750 --> 23:10.240
Hello.

23:10.510 --> 23:11.350
Since we're all here,

23:11.350 --> 23:13.080
let's take a picture together.

23:13.350 --> 23:13.720
Okay.

23:13.720 --> 23:14.720
Let's go.

23:16.030 --> 23:16.440
Come on.

23:16.440 --> 23:17.570
I'll take it for you.

23:18.480 --> 23:18.940
Come on.

23:20.550 --> 23:21.160
Ready?

23:21.400 --> 23:22.240
Stand still.

23:23.680 --> 23:25.200
3, 2, 1.

23:25.350 --> 23:26.350
Smile!

23:27.240 --> 23:28.200
Good shot!

23:31.600 --> 23:31.970
Wait.

23:32.000 --> 23:33.330
Someone slashed my bag!

23:35.000 --> 23:35.960
Who was it?

23:35.980 --> 23:37.510
Who stole my wallet?

23:37.600 --> 23:37.930
Hey!

23:37.960 --> 23:38.750
Who was it?

23:38.880 --> 23:39.350
Who?

23:39.350 --> 23:39.960
That's enough, Wei.

23:39.960 --> 23:41.020
When did it happen?

23:41.350 --> 23:42.680
Was it when we were leaving the station,

23:42.680 --> 23:43.480
or on the train?

23:43.480 --> 23:44.030
When I got off the train,

23:44.030 --> 23:45.070
it was still there.

23:45.070 --> 23:45.880
Did someone bump into you

23:45.880 --> 23:47.160
when you left the train station?

23:47.160 --> 23:47.480
Yes.

23:50.070 --> 23:50.590
Sorry, sorry.

23:50.590 --> 23:50.960
Hey.

23:52.960 --> 23:53.640
People in Longcheng

23:53.640 --> 23:54.920
are too savage.

23:54.920 --> 23:55.720
I just got off the train,

23:55.720 --> 23:56.920
and I get a "welcome gift" like this.

23:56.920 --> 23:57.520
Young man,

23:57.680 --> 23:58.880
watch your language.

23:59.030 --> 24:00.680
People in Longcheng aren't like that.

24:00.680 --> 24:02.030
Those are just a few bad apples.

24:02.030 --> 24:02.880
S-Stop talking.

24:02.880 --> 24:04.340
Let's help Wei look for it.

24:04.480 --> 24:05.480
-Okay.
-Mrs. Liu.

24:05.590 --> 24:06.320
Don't worry.

24:06.680 --> 24:07.610
Leave this to me.

24:08.240 --> 24:09.750
Aren't you guys going to Shengcheng?

24:09.750 --> 24:11.160
Take Yong's car

24:11.180 --> 24:11.910
and go ahead.

24:12.920 --> 24:13.920
Rest assured,

24:13.960 --> 24:15.750
we'll definitely find the wallet for you.

24:15.750 --> 24:16.830
Once we find it,

24:16.920 --> 24:18.780
we'll take the bus to Shengcheng.

24:18.920 --> 24:19.880
I don't want people saying

24:19.880 --> 24:21.350
that folks in Longcheng aren't honorable.

24:21.350 --> 24:22.070
Forget it, forget it.

24:22.070 --> 24:23.270
Let's not trouble this young lady.

24:23.270 --> 24:24.550
Okay, we'll do as you say.

24:24.550 --> 24:25.070
Wei,

24:25.270 --> 24:26.350
Bai is my

24:26.350 --> 24:27.200
most reliable friend.

24:27.200 --> 24:27.920
Trust her.

24:29.110 --> 24:29.550
Okay.

24:29.920 --> 24:30.780
All right then.

24:30.890 --> 24:31.440
Give that to me.

24:31.440 --> 24:32.430
My car is right over there.

24:32.430 --> 24:32.830
Take this suitcase.

24:32.830 --> 24:33.200
Here.

24:33.200 --> 24:34.060
Let me get that.

24:34.160 --> 24:34.510
Here.

24:35.640 --> 24:36.070
Then you guys...

24:36.070 --> 24:37.200
Don't worry, Mrs. Liu.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.000
See you later.

24:38.240 --> 24:38.640
Go on.

24:38.640 --> 24:39.550
Be careful.

24:39.790 --> 24:40.840
See you later.

24:43.760 --> 24:45.000
Bai, how are we going to find it?

24:45.000 --> 24:45.600
Follow me.

24:48.740 --> 24:49.540
Let's go, Mom.

24:52.030 --> 24:53.830
Let's wait for them a bit longer.

24:55.550 --> 24:56.880
From what Bai said just now,

24:56.880 --> 24:58.740
she seems to know who the thief is.

24:58.920 --> 25:00.400
It's the thugs

25:00.400 --> 25:01.460
around the train station.

25:01.460 --> 25:03.200
Bai used to do business here,

25:03.200 --> 25:04.590
so she's dealt with them.

25:04.590 --> 25:05.510
When I came here before,

25:05.510 --> 25:06.970
they also gave me trouble.

25:07.000 --> 25:08.200
Bai took care of it all.

25:08.200 --> 25:08.930
Don't worry.

25:09.880 --> 25:11.110
So the train station has become

25:11.110 --> 25:12.570
their lawless territory?

25:12.720 --> 25:13.920
Is there no one to keep them in check?

25:13.920 --> 25:15.790
Someone will deal with them
sooner or later.

25:15.790 --> 25:16.320
Let's go.

25:16.880 --> 25:17.410
Let's go.

25:18.440 --> 25:18.970
Let's go.

25:20.920 --> 25:21.380
Sis Bai.

25:21.400 --> 25:21.920
Sorry I was being rude

25:21.920 --> 25:23.000
just now.

25:23.120 --> 25:24.160
Let me introduce myself properly.

25:24.160 --> 25:24.890
I'm Kang Wei.

25:25.000 --> 25:26.680
I'm Zhou Cheng's childhood friend.

25:26.680 --> 25:27.590
I've heard how

25:27.590 --> 25:28.400
you stuck your neck out

25:28.400 --> 25:29.530
for Xiaolan before.

25:29.530 --> 25:30.160
I've heard a lot about you.

25:30.160 --> 25:31.440
No big deal.

25:34.200 --> 25:34.750
This wallet

25:34.750 --> 25:35.350
is not bad.

25:35.830 --> 25:36.960
It has a lot of money.

25:37.400 --> 25:37.920
Cao Liu!

25:39.920 --> 25:40.920
That's my wallet!

25:44.830 --> 25:45.830
Get out of the way!

25:47.640 --> 25:48.770
Sis Bai, wait for me!

26:04.030 --> 26:05.110
You bastard!

26:05.960 --> 26:07.350
What are you doing? What are you doing?

26:07.350 --> 26:07.960
Bastard!

26:07.980 --> 26:09.790
You son of a bitch,
give me back my wallet!

26:09.790 --> 26:11.990
What are you talking about?
Shoo, shoo.

26:13.160 --> 26:13.880
Ke Yixiong!

26:14.680 --> 26:15.720
Boss! Boss! Boss!

26:15.920 --> 26:17.160
Keep going.

26:24.750 --> 26:25.200
Xiong.

26:30.720 --> 26:31.650
I'm telling you,

26:31.790 --> 26:33.250
this better be important.

26:33.550 --> 26:35.080
Or else this round is on you.

26:35.240 --> 26:36.070
Boss.

26:36.850 --> 26:37.500
Fei stole

26:37.520 --> 26:38.640
a wallet
from one of Bai Zhenzhu's friends.

26:38.640 --> 26:40.100
They chased him down here.

26:46.100 --> 26:47.360
That woman is here too?

26:47.520 --> 26:48.690
It seems so.

26:48.720 --> 26:49.860
They were together.

26:50.960 --> 26:51.790
Ke Yixiong!

26:52.510 --> 26:53.510
You bastard!

26:54.440 --> 26:55.200
Hurry up!

26:55.440 --> 26:56.900
Give the wallet back to me!

26:57.110 --> 26:58.440
Give me back the wallet!

27:03.350 --> 27:03.960
Ms. Bai.

27:04.960 --> 27:06.960
You brought a lackey with you today?

27:07.160 --> 27:07.880
Shut up.

27:08.690 --> 27:10.020
Give me back the wallet.

27:11.480 --> 27:12.640
My brother

27:13.010 --> 27:14.670
picked up your wallet for you.

27:14.690 --> 27:16.790
You're not going to even say "thank you?"

27:16.790 --> 27:18.170
He stole it.

27:18.240 --> 27:19.640
Who said you could speak?

27:28.160 --> 27:28.790
Ms. Bai,

27:29.480 --> 27:31.160
you used to be just

27:31.160 --> 27:33.030
a fruit seller at the train station.

27:33.030 --> 27:34.890
You went to Shengcheng 4 years ago

27:35.030 --> 27:36.490
and started to make it big.

27:37.100 --> 27:38.960
Someone who just knows martial arts,

27:38.960 --> 27:39.640
how could you have

27:39.640 --> 27:40.830
any business sense?

27:43.310 --> 27:44.270
If you ask me,

27:45.440 --> 27:46.720
it was this friend

27:47.310 --> 27:49.640
who introduced you to Shengcheng, right?

27:51.680 --> 27:53.140
What are you trying to say?

27:54.400 --> 27:56.160
Nothing much.

27:56.640 --> 27:59.000
I'm just quite interested

27:59.550 --> 28:00.510
in this friend.

28:01.270 --> 28:03.200
We should all make money together.

28:03.920 --> 28:06.070
Ms. Bai, would you do me the honor

28:06.550 --> 28:08.000
of introducing me

28:08.590 --> 28:09.510
to this friend?

28:19.920 --> 28:21.250
Who do you think you are?

28:21.920 --> 28:24.030
She runs a legitimate business.

28:29.550 --> 28:31.480
Ms. Bai, you've made a lot of money,

28:31.510 --> 28:33.370
but your words are still so harsh.

28:36.030 --> 28:37.030
However,

28:38.750 --> 28:40.000
you are generous.

28:40.680 --> 28:42.510
Just pass on a message for me.

28:48.680 --> 28:50.000
Come by often!

28:55.400 --> 28:56.160
Him?

28:56.400 --> 28:57.310
A hero?

28:57.720 --> 28:58.920
More like a disgrace.

28:58.960 --> 29:00.270
He's just a local thug.

29:00.920 --> 29:02.790
He's basically the boss

29:02.790 --> 29:04.400
of the thugs around the train station.

29:04.400 --> 29:05.550
He acts all tough,

29:06.110 --> 29:07.570
but he's actually a loser!

29:08.400 --> 29:10.310
Everyone else has legitimate businesses,

29:10.310 --> 29:11.910
but he's still a petty thief.

29:12.070 --> 29:14.310
And he wants to get to know Xiaolan?

29:14.510 --> 29:15.590
Dream on!

29:15.920 --> 29:16.680
Exactly!

29:17.510 --> 29:19.000
The bus to Shengcheng

29:19.000 --> 29:20.030
runs every 3 hours.

29:20.030 --> 29:21.030
We have some time.

29:21.070 --> 29:23.600
Let me take you
to try some local specialties.

29:24.280 --> 29:25.590
Coming through. Make way.

29:25.590 --> 29:26.030
Watch out.

29:26.030 --> 29:26.440
We're here.

29:26.440 --> 29:27.100
Take a look.

29:31.480 --> 29:32.030
Sis Bai,

29:32.030 --> 29:33.200
the variety of breakfast

29:33.200 --> 29:33.930
you have here

29:34.130 --> 29:35.080
is q-quite the spread.

29:35.080 --> 29:36.350
That's not even all of it.

29:36.350 --> 29:37.660
There are tons of options.

29:37.660 --> 29:39.680
Seafood porridge,
pork and preserved egg porridge,

29:39.680 --> 29:40.680
beef porridge with egg...

29:40.680 --> 29:41.740
All kinds. Come on.

29:42.550 --> 29:42.920
Sis Bai,

29:42.920 --> 29:44.420
you're rattling off the menu like a pro.

29:44.420 --> 29:45.820
You're making me hungry.

29:46.390 --> 29:47.650
Let me have some water.

29:48.200 --> 29:49.750
This isn't for drinking.

29:49.960 --> 29:50.690
Give it to me.

29:55.440 --> 29:56.350
There are many migrant workers

29:56.350 --> 29:57.480
here in Yuesheng now.

29:57.480 --> 29:58.000
Doing this

29:58.000 --> 29:59.440
is more hygienic.

30:00.270 --> 30:00.720
Here.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.450
Hello. What would you like?

30:02.600 --> 30:03.860
One seafood porridge,

30:05.200 --> 30:06.000
chicken feet,

30:07.160 --> 30:08.420
and shrimp dumplings.

30:08.590 --> 30:09.640
Looks delicious.

30:09.640 --> 30:09.960
Okay.

30:09.960 --> 30:11.620
Are you a college student too?

30:11.680 --> 30:12.510
Me? No way.

30:12.510 --> 30:14.480
You can't just get into college.

30:14.640 --> 30:15.640
I graduated
from a technical middle school.

30:15.640 --> 30:17.240
I've been working for years.

30:17.860 --> 30:19.210
Since you're out here traveling,

30:19.210 --> 30:20.340
what about your job?

30:20.590 --> 30:22.310
My job has no future.

30:22.550 --> 30:23.860
It's not as good
as being self-employed like you.

30:23.860 --> 30:24.860
Xiaolan told me

30:24.960 --> 30:26.680
you have a stall in Shengcheng

30:26.830 --> 30:28.630
and that your business is great.

30:28.640 --> 30:30.600
It's thanks to meeting Xiaolan back then.

30:30.600 --> 30:31.790
She told me to take Longcheng's

30:31.790 --> 30:32.650
cheap trousers

30:32.860 --> 30:35.660
to resell them
at Shengcheng construction sites.

30:35.680 --> 30:36.880
I got

30:36.880 --> 30:38.020
the Border Permit.

30:38.240 --> 30:39.510
I've been to Shengcheng a few times.

30:39.510 --> 30:41.070
But it's all construction sites

30:41.070 --> 30:42.310
still building things up.

30:42.310 --> 30:43.570
What business can I do?

30:48.640 --> 30:49.070
This.

30:50.110 --> 30:52.160
I'm not cut out for the clothing business.

30:52.160 --> 30:54.220
Maybe I should learn pig butchering.

30:54.480 --> 30:56.790
Shengcheng Special Zone
is full of construction sites.

30:56.790 --> 30:57.350
That means

30:57.350 --> 30:58.920
there are construction workers everywhere.

30:58.920 --> 30:59.720
Where there are people,

30:59.720 --> 31:00.720
there's a market.

31:00.920 --> 31:02.790
Shangdu is an established city, after all.

31:02.790 --> 31:04.510
I stock mid-to-high-end goods there.

31:04.510 --> 31:05.920
In Shengcheng, we need to do the opposite.

31:05.920 --> 31:06.880
We need to focus on high volume,

31:06.880 --> 31:08.160
good quality, and low prices.

31:08.160 --> 31:09.490
These cheap dress pants

31:09.590 --> 31:10.590
would be perfect.

31:11.720 --> 31:14.160
Will... Will this really work?

31:14.800 --> 31:16.520
Dress pants, 70 a dozen!

31:16.590 --> 31:18.070
The more you buy, the cheaper I can go!

31:18.070 --> 31:19.270
Come take a look!

31:19.750 --> 31:20.130
Take a look

31:20.130 --> 31:20.680
at this fabric.

31:20.680 --> 31:22.640
How much off if I buy in bulk?

31:23.550 --> 31:24.440
If you buy 100,

31:24.750 --> 31:26.000
I'll give you 50% off.

31:27.590 --> 31:28.270
50% off?

31:28.680 --> 31:29.310
Trust me.

31:29.550 --> 31:31.150
I'll put up half the capital.

31:33.510 --> 31:34.000
Boss!

31:34.160 --> 31:35.030
I'll take 100!

31:35.240 --> 31:35.840
Of course!

31:37.350 --> 31:38.790
It's thanks to Xiaolan's advice;

31:38.790 --> 31:40.480
otherwise, the person you see now

31:40.480 --> 31:42.340
would just be Sis Bai the butcher.

31:52.070 --> 31:52.650
Sis Bai,

31:52.920 --> 31:53.830
Shengcheng is pretty close

31:53.830 --> 31:55.110
to Longcheng,

31:55.130 --> 31:56.660
but it's really different.

31:56.890 --> 31:57.520
Yeah.

31:57.550 --> 32:00.200
Longcheng developed
earlier than Shengcheng.

32:00.200 --> 32:02.460
But Shengcheng has more room for growth.

32:02.560 --> 32:04.160
That's what Xiaolan told me.

32:04.830 --> 32:05.790
Even though she's only

32:05.790 --> 32:07.200
been here a few times for stock,

32:07.200 --> 32:08.000
she seems to know this place

32:08.000 --> 32:08.930
better than I do.

32:09.480 --> 32:11.680
Is Xiaolan really moving to Shengcheng?

32:11.680 --> 32:13.540
I haven't heard Cheng mention it.

32:13.590 --> 32:15.510
I thought
she was just visiting for a few days.

32:15.510 --> 32:17.440
Maybe she hasn't decided yet.

32:19.400 --> 32:19.860
By the way,

32:19.860 --> 32:20.320
Sis Bai,

32:20.440 --> 32:22.350
y-you always talk about how amazing

32:22.350 --> 32:23.550
the Renmin Bridge is.

32:23.640 --> 32:24.270
Where is it?

32:24.270 --> 32:25.130
What's it like?

32:25.350 --> 32:25.750
Look!

32:26.240 --> 32:27.440
Once we cross this bridge,

32:27.440 --> 32:28.310
you'll see it.

32:28.470 --> 32:30.810
[Welcome to
Renmin Bridge Smallware Market]

32:28.760 --> 32:33.090
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

32:33.120 --> 32:36.710
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

32:37.570 --> 32:41.470
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

32:42.040 --> 32:45.310
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

32:45.900 --> 32:49.770
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

32:50.440 --> 32:54.880
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

32:54.910 --> 32:58.870
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

32:57.270 --> 32:59.000
Don't miss out!

32:59.350 --> 33:00.440
These are imported goods!

32:59.530 --> 33:04.090
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

33:00.440 --> 33:02.110
Look how stretchy they are!

33:02.240 --> 33:03.570
They're great. Buy one!

33:03.640 --> 33:05.270
This is the latest style from Gangdao!

33:04.600 --> 33:08.720
♪ The road ahead is full of storms ♪

33:05.270 --> 33:06.440
Bell-bottoms!

33:06.640 --> 33:07.830
Do you want any cassettes?

33:07.830 --> 33:09.250
We have Jacky Cheung and Andy Lau!

33:09.250 --> 33:12.630
♪ I'll get by them one by one ♪

33:09.550 --> 33:11.410
Hey pretty lady, come take a look.

33:11.590 --> 33:12.720
You're so pretty,

33:12.750 --> 33:13.620
and your voice is so sweet.

33:13.620 --> 33:17.630
♪ We'll guard each other
on the road ahead ♪

33:13.920 --> 33:14.920
We can do 180 yuan.

33:14.960 --> 33:15.480
How much?

33:15.480 --> 33:16.310
That's too expensive.

33:16.310 --> 33:17.270
That's half a month's wages!

33:17.270 --> 33:18.110
Too expensive.

33:18.110 --> 33:19.160
That year, when Zhenzhu and I

33:18.650 --> 33:21.420
♪ Don't be afraid of the long path ♪

33:19.160 --> 33:20.480
first came to Renmin Bridge,

33:20.480 --> 33:22.050
they only sold cheap goods around here.

33:22.050 --> 33:25.760
♪ With you,
there won't be despair on this path ♪

33:22.110 --> 33:23.160
Later, as more and more people

33:23.160 --> 33:23.920
came here to shop,

33:23.920 --> 33:24.790
these trendy clothes

33:24.790 --> 33:26.250
started selling well too.

33:26.590 --> 33:27.880
I finally found you!

33:27.920 --> 33:29.000
Is the luggage dropped off?

33:29.000 --> 33:29.510
Yes.

33:29.550 --> 33:31.280
They are all in the guesthouse.

33:31.590 --> 33:33.480
It's my first time here too.

33:33.750 --> 33:34.950
It's quite bustling.

33:35.140 --> 33:35.670
Mrs. Liu.

33:35.960 --> 33:36.680
Look at these.

33:36.680 --> 33:37.880
They must be imports.

33:39.480 --> 33:40.030
Xiaolan!

33:40.790 --> 33:41.510
Coming!

33:41.590 --> 33:42.350
Let's go, Mom.

33:42.350 --> 33:42.750
Yong.

33:47.010 --> 33:48.200
This is my stall right here.

33:48.200 --> 33:48.800
Come look.

33:49.160 --> 33:49.680
You're back!

33:49.680 --> 33:50.140
Senior!

33:50.440 --> 33:51.160
I'll be going then.

33:51.160 --> 33:52.400
Thanks, Senior.

33:52.400 --> 33:53.270
Thank you.

33:53.480 --> 33:54.070
Have a good time here

33:54.070 --> 33:54.590
with your friends.

33:54.590 --> 33:55.200
We will.

33:55.590 --> 33:56.120
Bye-bye.

33:57.000 --> 33:57.530
Mrs. Liu,

33:57.590 --> 33:58.270
have some

33:58.650 --> 33:59.110
herbal tea.

33:59.110 --> 33:59.570
Thanks.

33:59.590 --> 34:00.510
I can't handle this.

34:00.510 --> 34:01.880
It's all over the streets in Longcheng.

34:01.880 --> 34:03.310
I just can't get used to it.

34:03.310 --> 34:04.840
I still prefer plain water.

34:04.880 --> 34:05.680
Mom, try it.

34:05.830 --> 34:07.000
When I stock up in Longcheng,

34:07.000 --> 34:07.790
I drink it often.

34:07.790 --> 34:08.400
Let me try.

34:12.070 --> 34:13.929
It tastes like Chinese medicine.

34:14.070 --> 34:15.190
It's okay. I can get it down.

34:15.190 --> 34:16.510
Yeah. The climate here

34:16.510 --> 34:17.440
is hot and humid.

34:17.440 --> 34:20.040
Drinking this
relieves the dampness and heat.

34:20.150 --> 34:20.679
Zhenzhu,

34:20.880 --> 34:22.070
I see that

34:22.070 --> 34:24.130
you're selling quite varied things.

34:24.409 --> 34:25.199
Yeah.

34:25.230 --> 34:27.190
At first, I only sold clothes.

34:27.400 --> 34:28.110
Then I realized

34:28.110 --> 34:30.150
there were
too many people selling clothes.

34:30.150 --> 34:31.630
So I just followed the trend.

34:31.630 --> 34:33.159
I sell whatever is popular.

34:33.510 --> 34:34.480
Is it profitable?

34:34.480 --> 34:36.630
I did make money.

34:37.630 --> 34:38.550
In Shengcheng,

34:38.840 --> 34:39.920
as long as you're not lazy

34:39.920 --> 34:40.760
and willing to learn,

34:40.760 --> 34:41.760
you won't starve.

34:43.000 --> 34:44.360
This place is interesting.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.230
Your stall is so big.

34:45.230 --> 34:47.030
Why don't you get a proper shop?

34:48.590 --> 34:49.320
Don't get me started.

34:49.320 --> 34:50.730
I wanted to get a shop too.

34:50.880 --> 34:51.920
But right now,

34:52.230 --> 34:54.440
though there are
"For Sale" signs on the shops,

34:54.440 --> 34:55.670
when you actually call,

34:55.670 --> 34:56.710
no one answers.

34:57.340 --> 34:58.300
After a while,

34:58.330 --> 34:59.790
a new tenant would move in.

34:59.800 --> 35:01.440
It's all done internally.

35:01.960 --> 35:02.510
Zhenzhu,

35:02.710 --> 35:04.030
you really need a shop.

35:04.200 --> 35:05.840
The scale will be different with a shop.

35:05.840 --> 35:07.900
You can't be a street vendor forever.

35:08.000 --> 35:09.110
I understand that.

35:09.590 --> 35:11.120
I'll figure something out.

35:11.550 --> 35:13.240
It's not that
I don't want to treat you to a big meal.

35:13.240 --> 35:14.360
It's just that at Renmin Bridge,

35:14.360 --> 35:15.190
you must try

35:15.190 --> 35:16.390
our local specialty—

35:16.480 --> 35:17.210
boxed meals!

35:17.360 --> 35:17.710
Come!

35:18.070 --> 35:19.670
Freshly made and piping hot!

35:19.960 --> 35:20.550
There's char siu.

35:20.550 --> 35:21.880
Here, come on.

35:36.760 --> 35:38.090
What do you want to have?

35:45.480 --> 35:46.410
You like it here?

35:47.800 --> 35:49.590
It's something I'm looking forward to.

35:49.590 --> 35:51.480
When I chose architecture,

35:52.150 --> 35:54.010
this was the future I envisioned.

35:54.840 --> 35:56.110
Noisy construction sites,

35:56.110 --> 35:56.800
sweat,

35:57.000 --> 35:57.590
and dust.

35:58.110 --> 35:59.440
I've only seen this on TV

35:59.440 --> 35:59.920
before.

36:00.280 --> 36:01.590
I never thought one day,

36:01.590 --> 36:02.280
I could finally

36:02.280 --> 36:03.480
stop being a bystander

36:03.480 --> 36:05.670
and become someone participating in it.

36:05.670 --> 36:06.710
I hope one day

36:06.880 --> 36:08.760
I can also design and build

36:08.760 --> 36:09.920
a house of my own.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.880
If you want to design houses,

36:12.400 --> 36:13.070
you'd have to go to

36:13.070 --> 36:14.400
a design institute
after graduating, right?

36:14.400 --> 36:16.760
Design institutes are so rigid.

36:17.030 --> 36:17.840
Who knows how long it'll take

36:17.840 --> 36:18.970
to achieve my dream.

36:19.230 --> 36:21.110
Shengcheng is developing fast.

36:21.440 --> 36:22.640
I need to speed up too.

36:23.560 --> 36:24.280
Sir,

36:24.440 --> 36:25.550
one char siu rice.

36:25.840 --> 36:26.770
Two. Make it two.

36:26.850 --> 36:28.230
Two? Okay, two char siu rice.

36:28.230 --> 36:29.760
Sir, I'm paying!

36:29.840 --> 36:31.110
Okay, sure!

36:33.070 --> 36:33.840
Try it, quick.

36:33.840 --> 36:34.150
Okay.

36:34.150 --> 36:35.590
Our char siu is delicious.

36:35.590 --> 36:36.400
Hurry up!

36:36.480 --> 36:37.550
Thank you, Mrs. Liu.

36:37.550 --> 36:38.320
Try it.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.280
It tastes different

36:39.280 --> 36:40.140
from back home.

36:40.920 --> 36:41.320
Try it.

36:43.280 --> 36:43.670
It's good.

36:43.670 --> 36:44.150
It is.

36:44.710 --> 36:45.480
What are your plans

36:45.480 --> 36:46.590
after we eat?

36:47.370 --> 36:47.920
Sis Bai,

36:48.190 --> 36:50.390
I want to try setting up a stall with you.

36:50.550 --> 36:51.710
Are you serious?

36:52.480 --> 36:54.550
Just don't complain that it's hard work.

36:54.550 --> 36:55.020
Xiaolan,

36:55.020 --> 36:55.710
I have to go back

36:55.710 --> 36:56.880
to the construction site later.

36:56.880 --> 36:58.150
You show Mom around.

37:03.030 --> 37:04.510
It's so beautiful!

37:07.030 --> 37:08.320
Be careful, Mom!

37:09.280 --> 37:10.510
So beautiful.

37:16.030 --> 37:16.760
Come up here.

37:21.920 --> 37:23.280
I never thought in this life

37:23.280 --> 37:24.880
I'd see such a beautiful sea.

37:25.480 --> 37:26.480
Why not?

37:26.800 --> 37:27.600
In the future,

37:27.800 --> 37:29.440
I'll take you to more places

37:29.550 --> 37:30.880
to see the bigger world.

37:32.320 --> 37:32.750
Mom,

37:33.150 --> 37:34.110
do you like it here?

37:34.110 --> 37:35.440
If you like it, I like it.

37:36.240 --> 37:37.030
Wherever you go,

37:37.030 --> 37:38.830
I'll follow and take care of you.

37:38.920 --> 37:40.000
Comrade Liu Fen,

37:40.510 --> 37:41.880
you're not my accessory.

37:41.880 --> 37:43.440
I want you to really like it.

37:43.920 --> 37:45.030
I really do.

37:46.480 --> 37:46.810
Okay!

37:47.250 --> 37:48.500
After I graduate,

37:48.670 --> 37:49.960
we'll move here to Shengcheng.

37:49.960 --> 37:51.400
When we live here then,

37:51.730 --> 37:53.060
we can be just like this,

37:53.280 --> 37:55.150
enjoying the breeze and seafood.

37:55.590 --> 37:56.250
How's that?

38:02.790 --> 38:03.670
Typhoon!

38:14.190 --> 38:15.510
We really need a shop.

38:15.760 --> 38:16.320
Otherwise, a simple rain

38:16.320 --> 38:18.120
can make life miserable for you.

38:18.150 --> 38:18.480
Yeah.

38:18.480 --> 38:20.010
It won't stop anytime soon.

38:21.760 --> 38:22.150
Wait.

38:22.510 --> 38:24.030
Cheng didn't bring umbrellas.

38:24.030 --> 38:24.760
The rain is so heavy.

38:24.760 --> 38:26.020
How will they get back?

38:29.760 --> 38:30.590
How did this rain

38:30.590 --> 38:31.920
just start pouring out of nowhere?

38:31.920 --> 38:33.840
With rain this heavy,
there won't be any cars.

38:33.840 --> 38:36.570
Let's wait for the rain
to let up a bit before we go.

38:37.550 --> 38:38.190
If the rain

38:38.190 --> 38:39.190
doesn't stop before dark,

38:39.190 --> 38:40.400
I'll go over there to make a call.

38:40.400 --> 38:40.760
Okay.

38:43.320 --> 38:43.670
Here.

38:43.800 --> 38:44.260
Hold on.

38:45.510 --> 38:46.000
Slowly.

38:46.550 --> 38:47.320
Slowly.

38:48.360 --> 38:49.890
Xiaolan, Zhou Cheng, look.

38:53.280 --> 38:54.030
Let's go take a look.

38:54.030 --> 38:54.590
Let's go.

38:57.760 --> 38:59.290
What's wrong? Are you okay?

38:59.400 --> 38:59.930
Comrade,

39:00.110 --> 39:01.040
do you need help?

39:01.110 --> 39:02.630
My boss's stomach is acting up.

39:02.630 --> 39:04.150
I want to take him to the clinic,

39:04.150 --> 39:05.410
but the car broke down.

39:05.710 --> 39:06.760
Here, give it to me.

39:06.760 --> 39:08.090
Help him up. Help him up.

39:08.630 --> 39:09.030
Here.

39:09.510 --> 39:10.510
There's one more umbrella.

39:10.510 --> 39:11.190
Be careful!

39:24.920 --> 39:25.520
It's okay.

39:26.920 --> 39:27.920
Are you all right?

39:28.110 --> 39:29.590
I'm sorry. Sorry. So sorry.

39:29.590 --> 39:30.760
It's fine. It's fine.

39:30.760 --> 39:31.110
Slow down.

39:31.110 --> 39:31.550
Let me do it.

39:31.550 --> 39:32.750
Thank you. Thank you.

39:34.070 --> 39:35.400
Wipe yourself off more.

39:35.440 --> 39:36.000
I'm fine now.

39:36.000 --> 39:36.600
Look how wet your hair is.

39:36.600 --> 39:37.190
Let me dry it for you.

39:37.190 --> 39:38.720
I'm fine. I'm okay. No need.

39:40.000 --> 39:40.550
Come here.

39:40.550 --> 39:41.760
For you to dry your clothes.

39:41.760 --> 39:42.480
Don't let yourselves collapse

39:42.480 --> 39:43.590
before the patient even recovers.

39:43.590 --> 39:44.550
Thank you, Doctor.

39:44.550 --> 39:45.880
He has acute gastritis.

39:46.030 --> 39:47.550
It's best not to take medicine
on an empty stomach.

39:47.550 --> 39:48.630
This is a small clinic.

39:48.630 --> 39:50.000
We don't have a cafeteria.

39:50.000 --> 39:51.030
We still need to find a way

39:51.030 --> 39:52.280
to get him something bland to eat.

39:52.280 --> 39:52.610
Okay.

39:56.000 --> 39:56.510
Please.

39:56.510 --> 39:57.570
Okay. Give it to me.

39:57.980 --> 39:59.560
Mrs. Liu, I'll go out

39:59.590 --> 40:00.110
to see if there is

40:00.110 --> 40:00.890
anything to cook porridge in.

40:00.890 --> 40:02.090
Okay, okay. Go ahead.

40:44.280 --> 40:45.280
Wang.

40:48.510 --> 40:49.230
Mr. Tang.

40:49.510 --> 40:50.320
You're awake.

40:53.140 --> 40:54.710
Wang went to borrow a phone.

40:56.400 --> 40:57.660
I'll go get the doctor.

41:16.070 --> 41:16.870
You're awake.

41:17.610 --> 41:18.470
How do you feel?

41:19.030 --> 41:19.830
I'm all right.

41:21.990 --> 41:23.250
How is it? Does it hurt?

41:23.510 --> 41:24.910
It doesn't hurt anymore.

41:25.030 --> 41:25.890
How about here?

41:27.230 --> 41:27.630
Nope.

41:28.280 --> 41:30.080
Being able to eat is a good thing.

41:30.440 --> 41:31.800
But you should treat

41:32.070 --> 41:34.310
your chronic stomach problem properly
when you have time.

41:34.310 --> 41:36.400
If you're fine, you can be discharged.

41:36.400 --> 41:38.000
Remember to eat on time back home.

41:38.000 --> 41:39.000
Stick to a light diet.

41:39.000 --> 41:39.330
Okay.

41:39.590 --> 41:40.510
Okay, thank you.

41:40.510 --> 41:41.150
Thank you, Doctor.

41:41.150 --> 41:42.080
You're welcome.

41:44.320 --> 41:45.180
Thank you, too.

41:45.510 --> 41:46.510
Don't mention it.

41:49.710 --> 41:51.040
My name is Tang Hong'en.

41:51.420 --> 41:52.420
My name is Liu Fen.

41:57.400 --> 41:58.590
Can you get me another bowl?

41:58.590 --> 41:59.840
Sure, no problem.

42:14.550 --> 42:15.440
It's a bit hot.

42:16.360 --> 42:16.880
Well...

42:19.800 --> 42:20.280
Well...

42:20.920 --> 42:21.580
Let me do it.

42:23.670 --> 42:24.030
Here.

42:24.760 --> 42:26.070
You're still on an IV drip.

42:26.070 --> 42:26.400
Here.

42:33.630 --> 42:34.000
Here.

42:45.670 --> 42:46.670
I'll do it myself.

42:48.280 --> 42:48.840
Thanks.

42:49.440 --> 42:49.840
Okay.

42:52.880 --> 42:53.480
Thank you.

43:01.190 --> 43:02.250
Careful, it's hot.

43:10.550 --> 43:11.510
May I ask,

43:12.590 --> 43:13.650
where are you from?

43:14.320 --> 43:15.880
We are from Anqing, Yunan.

43:16.960 --> 43:18.020
You are from Yunan?

43:20.630 --> 43:22.540
I'm quite familiar with that place.

43:22.540 --> 43:23.990
I used to work there.

43:24.320 --> 43:25.320
What a coincidence!
